    "title": "京东开放平台个人/个体店铺母婴/玩具乐器类目招商激励政策（2026.2.1-2026.4.30）",
    "followRuleId": "1333351393424031744",
    "content": "<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">为鼓励商家在京东开放平台积极经营母婴/玩具乐器一级类目，特制定激励政策，具体内容如下：</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">一、参与商家</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">限京东开放平台</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">母婴及玩具乐器&rdquo;一级类目<span style=\"color: #232930;\">下的个人/个体店铺</span>，且<span style=\"color: #232930;\">店铺完成入驻的时间应为2026年2月1日及以后</span>。<span style=\"color: black;\">店铺ID需符合下文中第二部分第5条所列适用范围，具体归属关系可咨询对接店铺/类目运营，结果以店铺/类目运营反馈为准。</span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">二、激励政策</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、激励周期：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2026</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">年2月1日00：00至2026年4月30日23：59（以下称为&ldquo;考核期&rdquo;）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、激励规则：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2026</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">年激励模式及返还模式，具体如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（1）激励模式：以销售 NET GMV（计算方式详见3、数据口径）为基础进行考核。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（2）返还模式：按考核期考核，并按周期整体达标档位发放。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（3）激励、返还金额以京东系统确认为准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、<span style=\"color: black;\">数据口径：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（1）销售 GMV口径：为实收 NET GMV，即考核期内店铺内下单，且在2026年5月26日之前完成的订单产生的GMV【须剔除退货、未确认收货，取消订单、虚拟商品订单，刷单等风控订单、使用优惠券金额的订单等】，考核周期结束后，次月进行数据计算。其中销售GMV剔除站外投放部分。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（2）销售类目口径：</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">仅统计店铺在一级类目玩具乐器、母婴（剔除<span style=\"color: #232930;\">三级类目=</span>儿童袜、儿童配饰、儿童内裤）下产生的销售情况。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、其它说明</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（1）已享受平台特殊费率的订单所产生的GMV均计入本政策进行达成考核，但不再给予特殊费率订单所产生gmv的本政策下返利。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（2）此政策实施期间不与其他新商激励政策同享。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（3）激励周期内，若商家中途关店则激励终止。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、<span style=\"color: black;\">具体返利政策：（0.6%交易服务费另行单独收取，GMV单位：人民币元）</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">注：店铺ID归属于京喜事业部下，具体店铺归属请咨询各店铺/类目运营，政策考核期内数据最终以平台数据为准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（1） 返还激励：以销售 GMV为基础进行考核，按照商品挂靠类目扣点做激励返还，激励支付形式为广告现金。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（2） 广告红包激励：以销售 GMV为基础进行考核，满足奖励周期内的销售GMV门槛即可获得对应广告红包奖励。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（3） 广告红包使用说明：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">①</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">政策奖金池400万(如遇上限，按店铺报名先后顺序发放)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">②</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">红包金额向下取整，如1000.6元，发放1000元</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">③</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">使用范围：全站营销、快车通用</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">④</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">有效期：到账后60天内，红包过期作废不予退还</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">⑤</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">消耗逻辑：红包需搭配现金按照1：1配比使用</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">⑥</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">发放逻辑：发放至广告投放现金消耗最高的京准通账号 </span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15.24%; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"15%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">考核周期</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.88%; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">奖励门槛</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 24.54%; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"24%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">激励1</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.32%; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">激励2</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15.24%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"15%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核档位1</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.88%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">NETGMV</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">＞5W</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 24.54%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"24%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">扣点全返 （广告现金形式返还，单商家封顶2W）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.32%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">广告红包10000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15.24%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"15%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核档位2</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.88%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">NETGMV</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">＞15W</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.32%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">广告红包30000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15.24%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"15%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核档位3</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.88%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">NETGMV</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">＞30W</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.32%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">广告红包60000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15.24%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"15%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核档位4</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.88%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">NETGMV</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">＞50W</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.32%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">广告红包100000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15.24%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"15%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核档位5</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.88%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">NETGMV</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">＞100W</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.32%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">广告红包200000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、政策发布期间如有策略调整，可能会对激励、返还政策做出调整、中止或终止，调整政策是否追溯适用以京东公告为准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、本次激励政策与其他新商激励政策均互斥，即参与此激励政策的商家将不再享受其他同期激励政策；</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">三、违约责任</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">若商家在激励周期内发生以下任一情形，则京东开放平台有权取消商家因此获得的</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">全部激励且不承担任何责任；如激励已发放，则京东开放平台有权自任意一笔待与商家结算的款项中或商家已缴纳的保证金中直接扣除激励金，不足抵扣的，京东开放平台有权保留继续追偿的权利。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家及其关联方采取不正当手段（如刷单、套券等）获取激励的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家存在恶意竞争、影响消费者权益、影响京东平台声誉等违反市场公平竞争原则、诚实信用原则、公序良俗的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、其余违反</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2754&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反《京东开放平台招商资 质标准细则》的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反其他京东平台规则的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"right\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"right\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2026</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">年2月1日</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
